overview: Princess tells the true story of former cabaret dancer Anna Lappalainen's redemptive struggle with insanity, who checked in to Finland's Kellokoski Psychiatric Hospital in 1945.
tagline: Happier than the rest of us?
cast: Katja Küttner|Samuli Edelmann|Krista Kosonen|Pirkka-Pekka Petelius|Peter Franzén
